firecracker-agent (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Implement gRPC server for Firecracker VM management
  * Add Firecracker API client with Unix socket communication
  * Add VM process lifecycle management (start, stop, kill)
  * Add network manager for TAP devices and bridge configuration
  * Add storage manager with overlay filesystem support (qcow2)
  * Add comprehensive test suite with 100+ test cases
  * Add configuration management with YAML support
  * Add structured logging with logrus
  * Add systemd service integration
  * Add complete documentation

 -- Antonio Pardo <apardo@spluca.org>  Tue, 03 Feb 2026 08:00:00 +0100
